@BASE_URL = http://localhost:3001

### Health Check
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/health

###

### Register - Create a new user
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe2",
  "email": "john.doe2@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login - Success
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Profile - Get user profile
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### LINKS ENDPOINTS (Requires Authentication)
### ============================================

###

### Create Link - Encurtar URL
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/links
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6ImNtbmdreG9wbzAwMDBvd2lqbjE0cWVqbTAiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImpvaG4uZG9lQGV4YW1wbGUuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc1MTQzOTIxLCJleHAiOjE3NzU3NDg3MjF9.V4Tqg0eVpx5Zj5oqjfclZM4mBONKy_hiJ3rOc6i1U-M

{
  "url": "https://github.com.br"
}

###

### Create Link - Invalid URL (should fail with 400)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/links
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "url": "not-a-valid-url"
}

###

### Create Link - Without auth (should fail with 401)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/links
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://example.com"
}

###

### List Links - Default pagination
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/links
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6ImNtbmdreG9wbzAwMDBvd2lqbjE0cWVqbTAiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImpvaG4uZG9lQGV4YW1wbGUuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc1MTQzOTIxLCJleHAiOjE3NzU3NDg3MjF9.V4Tqg0eVpx5Zj5oqjfclZM4mBONKy_hiJ3rOc6i1U-M

###

### List Links - Custom pagination
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/links?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get Link Stats - Replace SHORT_CODE with actual short code
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/links/4Me1LE/stats
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6ImNtbmdreG9wbzAwMDBvd2lqbjE0cWVqbTAiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImpvaG4uZG9lQGV4YW1wbGUuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc1MDk1NzMxLCJleHAiOjE3NzU3MDA1MzF9.7QrHjVkZCy5opNUQEapEKR-3O3vQqvr1zDMNi5GDa-s

###

### Get Link Stats - Non-existent link (should fail with 404)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/links/non-existent/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Delete Link - Replace LINK_ID with actual link ID
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/api/links/LINK_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Delete Link - Non-existent link (should fail with 404)
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/api/links/non-existent-id
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### REDIRECT ENDPOINT (Public - No Auth Required)
### ============================================

###

### Redirect - Short URL redirect (replace SHORT_CODE with actual code)
### This will redirect to the original URL with HTTP 302
### and register the click with IP and User-Agent
GET {{BASE_URL}}/4Me1LE

###

### Redirect - Non-existent short code (should fail with 404)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/invalidcode

###

### Redirect - With custom User-Agent header
GET {{BASE_URL}}/4Me1LE
User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36
